1
00:00:01,520 --> 00:00:02,520
Is your foot okay?

2
00:00:03,000 --> 00:00:04,000
Huh?

3
00:00:04,480 --> 00:00:06,320
I mean, are you sure your foot is alright?

4
00:00:06,600 --> 00:00:07,920
Yeah, it's perfectly fine.

5
00:00:08,320 --> 00:00:09,480
Hmm.

6
00:00:12,920 --> 00:00:13,920
Mizuki!

7
00:00:14,320 --> 00:00:15,760
Pfft!

8
00:00:18,800 --> 00:00:21,000
You two are so close.

9
00:00:32,760 --> 00:00:34,080
Yo!

10
00:00:35,280 --> 00:00:36,440
The hero has arrived!

11
00:00:37,920 --> 00:00:38,920
Hey, Iijima Hinata!

12
00:00:39,760 --> 00:00:40,400
Hey!

13
00:00:40,400 --> 00:00:41,880
That pass you made was legendary!

14
00:00:41,880 --> 00:00:43,160
You really should join a club.

15
00:00:43,880 --> 00:00:45,000
Thanks...

16
00:00:47,640 --> 00:00:48,760
Iijima Hinata was amazing too!

17
00:00:48,760 --> 00:00:50,240
Thank you.

18
00:00:53,360 --> 00:00:54,920
Are you blushing from all the praise?

19
00:00:56,120 --> 00:00:57,200
I am not...

20
00:00:57,480 --> 00:00:58,480
Why are you like this?

21
00:00:59,000 --> 00:01:00,760
Do you really not want to talk to me at school?

22
00:01:01,640 --> 00:01:03,040
It's not like that.

23
00:01:04,680 --> 00:01:06,560
I just don't like all the noise.

24
00:01:07,920 --> 00:01:08,920
Hmm.

25
00:01:12,320 --> 00:01:14,120
Alright, let's go. Time to head home.

26
00:01:14,400 --> 00:01:15,100
Iijima Hinata, walk with us!

27
00:01:15,160 --> 00:01:16,240
You guys go ahead!

28
00:01:25,580 --> 00:01:26,580
Kono Mizuki.

29
00:01:29,060 --> 00:01:30,540
Let's... walk home together.

30
00:01:34,000 --> 00:01:35,580
Yeah...
